				<p class="postmetadata">30.05.2012 (Norbert Rost) Kategorie: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/presseschau/" title="Alle Beiträge in Presseschau ansehen" rel="category tag">Presseschau</a>  &middot; Tags: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/aspo/" rel="tag">ASPO</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/daniele-ganser/" rel="tag">Daniele Ganser</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/dennis-meadows/" rel="tag">Dennis Meadows</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/euan-mearns/" rel="tag">Euan Mearns</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/wien/" rel="tag">Wien</a>  &middot; <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/2012/05/aspo-tagt-in-wien/#respond" title="Kommentiere ASPO tagt in Wien">Kommentieren &#187;</a> </p>

